> **__Helpful Commands__**
.tag:intro
**__Introduction__**
This channel contains a list of all Clue Chasers discord commands along with a brief summary of what they contain. Feel free to use any of the commands in the <#333343575737892864> channel.

.
> __**Information Hub**__
.tag:infohub
⬥ `!gathering` - Links to the gathering section. (Needs adding)
⬥ `!solving` - Links to the solving section. (Needs adding)
⬥ `!faq` - Links to the faq section section. (Needs adding)

.
> __**Globetrotter Outfit**__
.tag:goutfit
⬥ `!globeorder` - Lists the priority order in which piece should be unlocked first based on tier. (Needs adding)
⬥ `!gjacket` - Explains the globetrotter jacket. (Needs adding)
⬥ `!gbackpack` - Explains the globetrotter backpack. (Needs adding)
⬥ `!garms` - Explains the globetrotter arm guards. (Needs adding)
⬥ `!gshorts` - Explains the globetrotter shorts. (Needs adding)
⬥ `!gboots` - Explains the globetrotter boots. (Needs adding)

.
> __**Alchemical Items & Broadcasts**__
.tag:rewards
⬥ `!fortunates` - Lists every item that can be disassembled into a fortunate component. (Needs adding)

.
