> __**Spreadsheets**__
.tag:sheets
⬥ `!hof` - Generates a link to Hall of Fame.
⬥ `!mostbarrows` - Generates a list of players with the most of selected item.
⬥ `!mostshadow` - Generates a list of players with the most of selected item.
⬥ `!mostice` - Generates a list of players with the most of selected item.
⬥ `!most3a` - Generates a list of players with the most of selected item.
⬥ `!mostblood` - Generates a list of players with the most of selected item.
⬥ `!mostdruidic` - Generates a list of players with the most of selected item.
⬥ `!mostosh` - Generates a list of players with the most of selected item.
⬥ `!casketvalue` - Generates a list of the average casket value of each tier.

.
> __**Server Help**__
.tag:serverhelp
⬥ `!nav` - Lists some ways of navigating Clue Chasers. (Needs adding)
⬥ `!notrading` - Shows our server rules and explains that trading is not allowed in our channels. (Needs adding)
⬥ `!clue` - Generates an invite link for Clue Chasers. (Needs adding)
⬥ `!cluehelp` - Links the Clue help forum and questions channel. (Needs adding)
⬥ `!suggestion` - Links suggestions forum and offers examples of possible suggestions.
⬥ `!website` - Links the Clue Chasers website.
⬥ `!twitter` - Links the Clue Chasers twitter.

.
